channel.title: #317 Framework 'The After Years'
channel.description:
[center]
[b]The After Years[/b]
The After Years is a 317 private server which incorporates a blocking network system. It currently only supports login, but also has a base for decoding other transmissions such as packets. If you don't like it don't post. I'm just trying to be kind by releasing this, not that anyone will likely use it though. The project was named after the sequel to the original Final Fantasy II.
